                                   @{b}MTG Guide
                                   ---------@{ub}
                        Version 2.12 - 22 November 1997


          A complete database for Magic: The Gathering in Amiga Guide
          format, containing all cards from every expansion, including
          their description, official errata and changes, rulings etc.
          This database also contains the general rulings for playing
          the game itself.

                                @{" Take a look " link INHOUD}
                                @{" Feedback    " link FEEDBACK}


 @{b}THIS PRODUCT IS NOT PUBLISHED OR ENDORSED BY WIZARDS OF THE COAST, INC. (TM)@{ub}


         @{i}Wizards  of  the Coast, Deckmaster and Magic:  The Gathering
            are registered trademarks of Wizards of the Coast, Inc.
         Corresponding logos, the tap symbol and the mana symbols are
                   trademarks of Wizards of the Coast, Inc.
         Card  illustrations are copyright Wizards of the Coast, Inc.
         This product is in no way sponsored by Wizards of the Coast.@{iu}

@endnode
